      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just playing a role all the time. like i'm wearing this skin that doesn't even fit and everyone around me just expects me to keep performing. it's so exhausting. i don't think i have the energy to keep fighting for a version of me that the world might never even accept.",
